INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (390,1,'2011-03-06 20:07:25','2011-03-07 01:07:25','<h1>IACT Innovator\'s Challenge: Surgical Innovation</h1>\r\n<strong> </strong>Announcing the IACT Innovator\'s Challenge: Surgical Innovation!\r\n\r\n<strong>April 9, 2011\r\n9:30am - 5:00pm\r\nLocation:  115 Mervis Hall</strong>\r\n<strong>3950 Roberto Clemente Drive, Pittsburgh, PA 15213</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>The IACT Innovator\'s Challenge: Surgical Innovation is a student pitch competition that will expose students to the world of <strong>healthcare technology innovation</strong>.\r\n\r\nStudents will get the opportunity to:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Learn from expert business leaders, academic faculty, and clinical physicians;</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborate with passionate students from local universities, such as the University of Pittsburgh and Carnegie Mellon University;</li>\r\n	<li>Get mentored by accomplished professionals;</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch their concepts to an all-star judging panel.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThroughout the day, interdisciplinary teams of students will be tasked with identifying a problem within the realm of surgery and developing a unique solution. Teams will then give a 2.5 minute elevator pitch explaining the market and business opportunity while detailing how a team would proceed to make the concept a reality!\r\n\r\nJoin us for this exciting event.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Apply to the IACT Innovator’s Challenge: Surgical Innovation\" href=\"http://iactpgh.com/challenge/surgical/apply/\"><strong>Apply Now!</strong></a>','IACT Innovator\'s Challenge: Surgical Innovation','','publish','closed','closed','','surgical','','','2011-03-18 10:52:49','2011-03-18 14:52:49','',95,'http://iactpgh.com/?page_id=390',0,'page','',0),(373,1,'2011-01-15 17:54:24','2011-01-15 22:54:24','<h2>Apply to the Feb. 10 Surgical Innovation Event</h2>\r\nStudents, if you are interested in participating in the Surgical Innovation Event, submit your application below. A member of the IACT team will contact you about your application.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, contact <a href=\"mailto:info@iactpgh.com\">info@iactpgh.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<form action=\"../submit\" enctype=\"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\" method=\"post\">First Name:<input maxlength=\"45\" name=\"first_name\" size=\"45\" type=\"text\" /><br /><br />\r\n\r\nLast Name:<input maxlength=\"45\" name=\"last_name\" size=\"45\" type=\"text\" /><br /><br />\r\n\r\nUniversity:<select name=\"university\"> <option selected=\"selected\" value=\"blank\"></option> <option value=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</option> <option value=\"University of Pittsburgh\">University of Pittsburgh</option></select><br /><br />\r\n\r\nDepartment (e.g. School of Medicine, School of Computer Science, etc.):\r\n\r\n<input maxlength=\"120\" name=\"department\" size=\"45\" type=\"text\" /><br /><br />\r\n\r\nType of Student (e.g. Masters, M.D., Ph.D., etc):<input maxlength=\"45\" name=\"degree\" size=\"45\" type=\"text\" /><br /><br />\r\n\r\nE-mail:<input maxlength=\"120\" name=\"email\" size=\"45\" type=\"text\" /><br /><br />\r\n\r\nBriefly state your reason for wanting to attend the event:<textarea onkeydown=\"limitText(this.form.reason, this.form.countdown,2000);\" onkeyup=\"limitText(this.form.reason, this.form.countdown, 2000);\" cols=\"45\" rows=\"10\" name=\"reason\"></textarea>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-small;\">You have</span>\r\n\r\n<input name=\"countdown\" readonly=\"readonly\" size=\"3\" type=\"text\" value=\"2000\" /> characters left.\r\n<input name=\"submit\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" /> </form>','Apply to the Feb. 10 Surgical Innovation Event','','inherit','open','open','','250-revision-7','','','2011-01-15 17:54:24','2011-01-15 22:54:24','',250,'http://iactpgh.com/announcements/250-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(293,1,'2011-01-22 20:52:21','0000-00-00 00:00:00','Thank you to everyone who came to today\'s event!','Thank You - IACT Innovator\'s Challenge','','dra